What seemed sacrilegious for the Pope

00:05:08.790 --> 00:05:11.093
seemed perfectly reasonable for Elvis.

00:05:13.080 --> 00:05:15.980
I found pleasure in every
possible incarnation

00:05:15.980 --> 00:05:17.143
of Elvis's image.

00:05:18.227 --> 00:05:20.810
(bright music)

