Somebody had just shot off a flashbulb,

00:10:11.750 --> 00:10:16.620
I call this "Starburst", and
it was in sync to my shutter

00:10:16.620 --> 00:10:20.100
and it flared me out and
it made a great picture.

00:10:20.100 --> 00:10:23.080
And this is, here, I'm gonna
ask you a few questions,

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:26.600
what's going on here
with the motorcycle shot,

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:28.500
which is a well known shot?

00:10:28.500 --> 00:10:30.730
Why is he looking like that?

00:10:30.730 --> 00:10:33.330
Well, the question was, why
won't the motorcycle start,

00:10:33.330 --> 00:10:35.820
and the answer was, there
was no gas in the tank.

00:10:35.820 --> 00:10:39.270
Now Elvis always assumed
somebody's supposed to do it,

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:42.190
well they didn't, and then
eventually when they got the gas

00:10:42.190 --> 00:10:43.290
the motorcycle worked.

00:10:44.227 --> 00:10:46.743
That's the way it is with machinery.

00:10:48.170 --> 00:10:50.040
- [Annie] I disagreed.

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:52.230
There were a thousand answers.

00:10:52.230 --> 00:10:53.343
His was just one.

00:10:54.870 --> 00:10:56.750
I knew this image.

00:10:56.750 --> 00:11:01.150
I'd seen it on watches,
lunch boxes, t-shirts,

00:11:01.150 --> 00:11:03.250
and it was never about running out of gas.

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:10.360
Elvis was only 21, and
there I was, the same age.

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:17.400
I wish I could have asked
Elvis what he'd been thinking.

00:11:17.400 --> 00:11:19.403
Whether he knew he was no longer mortal.

00:11:21.540 --> 00:11:22.803
I'd never get the chance.

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:28.190
I was born too late, born
the same year Elvis died.

00:11:28.190 --> 00:11:31.220
So I'm left searching
his images for clues.

00:11:31.220 --> 00:11:35.137
(fans cheering and applauding)

00:11:37.461 --> 00:11:41.044
(camera shutters clicking)

00:11:45.900 --> 00:11:48.330
- Am I gonna sit down?

