First of all, I plead
innocent of all charges.

00:11:51.424 --> 00:11:52.850
(audience laughs)

00:11:52.850 --> 00:11:53.750
- [Reporter] Are you satisfied

00:11:53.750 --> 00:11:55.140
with the image you've established?

