- Well the image is one thing

00:11:56.627 --> 00:11:58.530
and human being is another, you know.

00:11:58.530 --> 00:12:00.880
- [Reporter] How close
is the image to the man?

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:03.730
- It's very hard to live up
to an image, put it that way.

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:07.680
- [Reporter] What about
your image as a shy, humble-

