While the news cut straight to his answer,

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:18.092
here's what really happened.

00:12:18.092 --> 00:12:19.201
- [Reporter] Are you satisfied

00:12:19.201 --> 00:12:22.034
with the image you've established?

00:12:24.020 --> 00:12:26.160
- [Annie] The answer's not in his words,

00:12:26.160 --> 00:12:27.910
it's in what he does with his head.

00:12:28.840 --> 00:12:30.540
The moment Elvis looks behind him,

00:12:31.430 --> 00:12:35.356
as if looking for his image, then answers.

00:12:35.356 --> 00:12:38.460
(audience cheers and applauds)

