Isn't that the large part of his appeal?

00:13:02.060 --> 00:13:04.863
The belief that there's
still yet more to discover?

00:13:06.980 --> 00:13:10.093
It's these in between moments
I find most revealing.

00:13:12.090 --> 00:13:15.070
Now that Elvis the person
is no longer alive,

00:13:15.070 --> 00:13:17.743
Elvis's image can be whatever
anyone wants it to be.

00:13:18.580 --> 00:13:20.593
Perfect, immortal.

00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:25.430
It makes a whole new
kind of myth possible.

00:13:26.830 --> 00:13:28.543
Creates room for the imagination.

